The shrine's main hall was rebuilt in {{ill|1444|ja|1444th year }} (Bun'an 1, {{ill|Muromachi period|ja|室町時代}}), but was destroyed in {{ill|1944|ja|1944th year }} (Shōwa 19) due to a typhoon. The current structure was rebuilt after World War II.
